# Copy to .env and paste the APIM subscription key you receive on hackathon day.
# The key stays server-side: vite.config.ts injects it into proxied /llm requests.
# It is NOT prefixed with VITE_ on purpose — never expose it to the browser bundle.
# Restart `npm run dev` after changing this file by hand.
#
# Alternative: with the dev server already running, click "Add API key" in the
# AgentDock UI — it validates the key against APIM, activates it immediately (no
# restart), and writes it back here for next time.
APIM_KEY=
